This paper deals with the use of energy harvesting to mitigate jamming attacks in wireless networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), which deals with the transmission, processing, and utilization of information. The paper also involves network security, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The use of energy harvesting involves optimizing the use of resources, which falls under cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves strategic interaction between nodes, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with wireless networks, which falls under cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture).
